items.title: IT Q3 earnings season begins on a strong note as TCS, HCL Tech top estimates
items.description: IT sector's Q3 results show a positive start, with TCS and HCL Technologies exceeding revenue and profit expectations. HCL Tech recorded a nine-quarter high in new order bookings, while TCS maintained strong deal flow. Despite sustained new deals, TCS faces a revenue growth deceleration, raising concerns about deal ramp-up amid client delays.
